main event: An object described as a large ball of fire that sounded like an aircraft was observed over the treetops in Lakehurst, New Jersey in 1966.
interesting points: The object was observed for only about 10 seconds before going straight up.
There were conflicting details about the sighting, making the evaluation inconclusive.
The Air Force requested more information from the witnesses using a PTD Form 164.
The sighting was part of Project Blue Book, the historical U.S. Air Force program that investigated UFOs.
The report mentions that the object was observed under conditions of good visibility.
sighted object: a large ball of fire that sounded like an aircraft
